As just smaller than your fingers, the little monkey is crocheted by embroidery threads with joints, his arms, legs and tail can be movable, his eyes are sewn black cored plastics and stuffed by polyfil.

Size: Aprox.  1 inch ( 2.5 cm) tall in standing.

Perfect for any MICRO DOLLHOUSE or MINIATURE of your minis monkey collection, and is intended for adult collectors only, he should sit safely on a shelf or in a box to enjoy watching.

